snippet.title: Indie Game: Amanita August (Releasing March 6th!)
snippet.description:
#indiegame #visualnovel #horrorgaming 
Amanita August is an indie horror game/visual novel where you play as a cute little mushroom guy running a totally normal store and supplying the kingdom's chosen hero with everything she needs for her quest!

Releasing for free on March 6th on itch.io!

Trailer created by JakeMaster
